{"tid":1938280,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"將軍澳一帶現場","createTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T12:25:04.000Z","uid":226863,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b24c57a1730ef07736c83ef3a444687cc0372e93","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"陳彥霖離世半年網民悼念　防暴警截查帶走二人<br />\n<br />\n香港知專設計學院學生陳彥霖離世半年，有網民今日在知專發起悼念活動。在晚上7時許，大批防暴警員在知專設計學院及調景嶺站一帶戒備，有多名年輕人被警方截查。當中有2人疑因無帶身份證被警方帶走，被問是否作出拘捕時，警員表示：「私人嘢，唔答得。」<br />\n<br />\n大家集中討論"},{"pid":"2b6ce771c6f6c54221acaa2d44cbaa8e348b9da1","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e595b48618fec119130c94e80d4ee97a95dd649f","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"da8eeabb56b97c656c9f8e007ad50cbddd52fb7c","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bedcfcb297504ca06ecb4e9d34a33fc586dbb748","tid":1938280,"uid":319953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2787995f98c006e07cb6ea14efa3af09a04e5c67","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c765e76e31787f2a3506f25438304fd46ef0f91","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3095f8ab27f6b32318b7b768f5308b8676aac9b9","tid":1938280,"uid":226863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c9fe5cdbef9d010c8cd9e65ff43147d355809f65","tid":1938280,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2c68566c9bc70d78e367f664a5529f27bb44f66","tid":1938280,"uid":235501,"